 2024-03942024-04-19PSPC
ActNational Capital Act
SubjectOrder Approving that the NCC Extend the Lease with Au Feel de l'eau INC.
PrecisOrder approving that the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION grant two options to extend the lease with AU FEEL DE L’EAU INC. for the real property located on the shoreline of the Ottawa River, in Ottawa, Ontario, and Gatineau, Quebec, for a period of 5 years each, beginning on May 1, 2025 and May 1, 2030.
